《'''南国警察'''》（{{lang|en|''Southland''}}，又译《南城警事》、《洛城警事》）是[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]得主安·拜德曼全新创造的一部警匪类剧集。<ref name="nytimes">Wyatt, Edward. [http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/09/arts/television/09sout.html?ref=arts NBC's Latest Drama Has a (Temporary) Home] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/09/arts/television/09sout.html?ref=arts |date=20190929012312 }}, ''New York Times'', April 8, 2009. Accessed August 5, 2009.</ref> 全剧主要讲述了[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]警署的数位警探的工作和日常生活。

剧集第一季于2009年4月9日至5月21日在[[美国|美国]][[NBC|NBC]]台首播，共7集。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003122.html | title=NBC picks up 'Southland' | publisher=Variety | accessdate=2009-05-02 | date=May 1, 2009 | last=Littleton | first=Cynthia | last2=Schenider | first2=Michael}}</ref> 2009年10月8日，NBC宣布取消该剧第二季的播映计划。<ref name="andreeva">{{cite news| author= Andreeva, Nellie| title= Southland Cancelled| url= http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3ieb794c2afa55454155ab3cda7e6e78b4| publisher= The Hollywood Reporter| date= October 8, 2009| accessdate= 2009-10-16| archive-date= 2010-09-18| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100918120118/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3ieb794c2afa55454155ab3cda7e6e78b4| dead-url= no}}</ref>

随后，TNT电视台宣布买下该剧第二季的播映权，并于2010年1月12日起播映《南国警察》第一季全7集，并续订了第二季。<ref name="turner">{{cite web |url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=4777 |date=11/2/2009 |title=TNT Picks Up Acclaimed Drama SOUTHLAND |publisher=TNT |accessdate=2010-09-01 |archive-date=2010-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328154102/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=4777 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2010年4月26日，TNT电视台宣布它续订了《南国警察》的第三季，并将于2011年1月开播，共10集。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5111 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-09-01 |archive-date=2010-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100429143934/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5111 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年4月26日，TNT电视台宣布续订第三季，新季于2011年1月4日起上映，共10集。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5111 |title=Turner Newsroom: Home |publisher=News.turner.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-02 |archive-date=2010-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100429143934/http://news.turner.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=5111 |dead-url=no }}</ref>起续订要求削减预算，并相应缩减演出人员规模。<ref name="deadline.com">{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/05/southland-faces-budget-reduction-cast-trims-on-tnt/ |title=‘Southland’ Facing Budget & Cast Trims – |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-02 |archive-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206012551/http://www.deadline.com/2010/05/southland-faces-budget-reduction-cast-trims-on-tnt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年3月22日，该剧再次获得新一季的预定，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/03/22/tnt-renews-southland-for-a-fourth-season/86671 |title=Southland Renewed for Fourth Season by TNT - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2011-09-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308220844/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/03/22/tnt-renews-southland-for-a-fourth-season/86671/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>第四季于2012年1月17日开始上映，仍为10集。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tnt.tv/series/southland/ |title=TNT - Southland: Home |accessdate=2012-01-24 |archive-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402012942/http://www.tnt.tv/series/southland/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

